<br>
I just wanted to pop over and say hi. I also wanted to take this opportunity and explain a few events on the HKD calendar.  During the month of November I’m leading 6 HoT raids. I’ve also noticed that a few Amazon folks have signed up. Some of you may notice that you were bumped to non-participating. Fear not my friends. Many raids were pre-planned prior to HKD/Amazon talks. I hate changing the “rules” this late in the game. I would however like to apologize for excluding you on these raids. I’m eager to have you join us and look forward to many more open raids between the two of us. So please visit back often. Going forward I hope to lead and be part of many more raids. <br>
<br>
